3#ifndef __NVBIOS_I2C_H__
4#define __NVBIOS_I2C_H__
5enum dcb_i2c_type {
6 /* matches bios type field prior to ccb 4.1 */
7 DCB_I2C_NV04_BIT = 0x00,
8 DCB_I2C_NV4E_BIT = 0x04,
9 DCB_I2C_NVIO_BIT = 0x05,
10 DCB_I2C_NVIO_AUX = 0x06,
11 /* made up - mostly */
12 DCB_I2C_PMGR = 0x80,
13 DCB_I2C_UNUSED = 0xff
14};
15
16struct dcb_i2c_entry {
17 enum dcb_i2c_type type;
18 u8 drive;
19 u8 sense;
20 u8 share;
21 u8 auxch;
22};
23
24u16 dcb_i2c_table(struct nvkm_bios *, u8 *ver, u8 *hdr, u8 *cnt, u8 *len);
25u16 dcb_i2c_entry(struct nvkm_bios *, u8 index, u8 *ver, u8 *len);
26int dcb_i2c_parse(struct nvkm_bios *, u8 index, struct dcb_i2c_entry *);
27#endif
